<p>China’s Supreme People’s Court has overturned the death sentence of Canadian citizen Robert Lloyd Schellenberg, who faces drug-related charges in China. Canadian and legal sources said officials communicated the reversal on Friday. Many are reading the move as a possible sign that tensions between Ottawa and Beijing may be easing after years of strain.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/LJ_-cqLL6dT8r7IgRG1VsXrLhYPPtrXDwCHnSGQIoKD4HJ8Xn0I1Chw1MQIogr7dFNZ8mFvh5KWFTqTSEHC7LUSZAi9lJ5l8-e6-xx9jVpKWJeEwUqcepuSE2KuhlUKmS999XiavsLaVZUn6bPAmm9ehrLkJ0yd4NNngBtZ0Ltxxtdf96Mog6SSL7c6qpcId_V7-cwiD' alt='Robert Lloyd Schellenberg in 2019 during his retrial on drug-trafficking charges in a court in Dalian, China.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Case history: Schellenberg was detained in 2014 and later faced a retrial in Dalian in 2019, keeping the case in the international spotlight for years.</li><li>Lawyer’s account: Schellenberg’s lawyer, Zhang Dongshuo, said China’s Supreme People’s Court announced the reversal, highlighting that the change came from the country’s top judicial body.</li><li>Diplomatic backdrop: The Guardian noted that Canada–China ties “nosedived” in 2018, a key reason observers are viewing the ruling through a geopolitical lens.</li><li>Domestic politics angle: The New York Times called the reversal a “small win” for Canadian Prime Minister Mark Carney as he works to steady relations with Beijing.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Canadian officials (Guardian/CTV): A Canadian official confirmed the court overturned the death sentence. The Guardian framed the development as a possible sign of thawing ties as Mark Carney pushes to expand trade with Beijing. (<a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/feb/07/china-overturns-death-sentence-of-canadian-robert-lloyd-schellenberg-in-sign-of-diplomatic-thaw'>The Guardian</a>, <a href='https://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/article/china-overturns-death-sentence-for-canadian-in-drug-case/'>CTV News</a>)</li><li>Schellenberg’s lawyer (Zhang Dongshuo): Reached in Beijing on Saturday, Zhang said China’s highest court announced the reversal on Friday. (<a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/feb/07/china-overturns-death-sentence-of-canadian-robert-lloyd-schellenberg-in-sign-of-diplomatic-thaw'>The Guardian</a>)</li><li>The New York Times framing: The New York Times emphasized that the ruling followed a recent meeting between China’s and Canada’s top leaders, which it said helped contribute to a thaw in relations. (<a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/06/world/asia/china-canada-death-sentence-overturned.html'>The New York Times</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/china-overturns-death-sentence-for-canadian-in-drug-case'>China overturns death sentence for Canadian in drug case</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/feb/07/china-overturns-death-sentence-of-canadian-robert-lloyd-schellenberg-in-sign-of-diplomatic-thaw'>China overturns death sentence of Canadian in sign of diplomatic thaw</a> - theguardian.com</li><li><a href='https://www.reddit.com/r/worldnews/comments/1qxxezt/china_overturns_death_sentence_for_canadian/'>China overturns death sentence for Canadian Robert Schellenberg</a> - reddit.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/06/world/asia/china-canada-death-sentence-overturned.html'>China Reverses Death Sentence for Canadian in a Small Win for Carney</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/article/china-overturns-death-sentence-for-canadian-in-drug-case/'>China overturns the capital punishment for Canadian citizen Robert Lloyd Schellenberg after he was detained on drug trafficking charges in 2014.</a> - ctvnews.ca</li></ul>